The landing page itself acts as article 00.

## Status language

Every later article must label:

- **Accepted design:** canonical architecture or language contract
- **Current implementation:** behaviour recorded by the progress matrix
- **Queued or active implementation:** named roadmap work
- **Deferred or outside scope:** intentionally postponed or rejected design

Link to the progress matrix and roadmap. Do not copy either document into the
articles. Keep accepted architecture as the main teaching path.

